				<wikidot:authorName>TheHouseOfBalloons</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3369416</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It means an anomaly that sort of self-contains itself. Like in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3700">SCP-3700</a> the two entities are considered hiemal because they are pretty much self-contained and don't cause a lot of danger to the general population. I like to think of it as a safe/keter mixed class.</p> 
				 	]]>
