				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381818#post-3725245</guid>
				<title>SCP-3787: The Horse Meme</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5381818/scp-3787#post-3725245</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 01 Mar 2018 03:24:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-3787:</strong> The Horse Meme<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>Okay, here's my second SCP. This existed in many different iterations between May 2017 and when I posted it, and between then and now. Before I posted it, I had adapted it to fit under the Hiemal classification after I was inspired by these two articles:</p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3240">SCP-3240</a></strong>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" >AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span></li> <li><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3700">SCP-3700</a></strong>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span></li> </ul> <p>Another inspiration here was the <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/antimemetics-division-hub">Antimemetics Division</a></strong>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" >qntm</a></span>. Given when this SCP was conceived, however, it deviates significantly from qntm's portrayal of the Division.</p> <p>Per <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span>'s recommendation, this article now fits under the Archon classification.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;and&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" >minmin</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phamtomguy" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187915&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="PhamtomGuy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187915)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phamtomguy" >PhamtomGuy</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/endingparadox" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3701955&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="EndingParadox" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3701955)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/endingparadox" >EndingParadox</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smlt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3291477&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="smlt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3291477)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smlt" >smlt</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601672550" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/u